---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import SchemaMarkup from "../../components/SchemaMarkup.astro";
import Icon from "../../components/Icon.astro";

// Make this page dynamic via SSR
export const prerender = false;

const publishDate = new Date("November 9 2026");
const author = "The Valley Clean Team";
const readTime = "5 min read";

const isPublished = new Date().getTime() >= publishDate.getTime();

---

<BaseLayout
  title="Military Precision Cleaning: Veterans Day"
  description={isPublished ? "Veterans Day feature: how The Valley Clean Team's veteran-owned values drive military-precision cleaning standards across Huntsville, the Shoals & Nashville, TN." : "Coming Soon: Why We Value Military-Precision Accountability (Veterans Day Feature)"}
  noindex={!isPublished}
  ogImage="https://storage.googleapis.com/msgsndr/iKQIBhpKVL2XVPgU7HMd/media/6920802945dc047d65b4ec5d.png"
>
  <SchemaMarkup
    type="article"
    title="Why We Value Military-Precision Accountability (Veterans Day Feature)"
    description="A Veterans Day feature: Learn why The Valley Clean Team values military precision and accountability, and how it translates to superior cleaning services."
    publishDate="November 9 2026"
    author={author}
  />
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="pt-24 pb-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-900 via-gray-800 to-gray-900">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center">
        <span class="inline-block px-4 py-2 bg-[#FFA985]/20 text-[#FFA985] rounded-full text-sm font-medium mb-6">
          Brand Story/Trust
        </span>
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-white mb-6 leading-tight">
          Why We Value Military-Precision Accountability (Veterans Day Feature)
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          {isPublished ? "Expert Cleaning Guide" : "Coming November 9 2026."}
        </p>
        <div class="flex items-center justify-center space-x-4 text-gray-400 mb-8">
          <span>November 9 2026</span>
          <span>•</span>
          <span>{readTime}</span>
          <span>•</span>
          <span>By {author}</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Main Content Toggle based on Published Date -->
  {isPublished ? (
    <article class="py-16 bg-white">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
          <!-- TODO: REPLACE THIS SECTION WITH YOUR ACTUAL BLOG CONTENT -->
          <h2>Why Does The Valley Clean Team Value Military-Precision Accountability?</h2>
<p><strong>The Valley Clean Team embraces military-precision accountability because it ensures that every cleaning task is executed with unmatched accuracy and reliability. As a veteran-owned company, we believe in the power of discipline and integrity to deliver exceptional results and earn our clients' trust. Our commitment to these values guarantees that every home and office in The Shoals & Surrounding Areas receives the meticulous care it deserves.</strong></p>

<h3>Understanding Military-Precision Accountability</h3>
<p>At The Valley Clean Team, we don't just clean; we execute with purpose and precision. This approach is deeply rooted in military principles, where every action is deliberate, and every outcome is measured against the highest standards. But what does this mean for our clients in The Shoals & Surrounding Areas?</p>

<h4>The Core of Our Commitment</h4>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Accountability:</strong> We take complete ownership of our work. If a task isn't performed to our standards, we address it immediately.</li>
  <li><strong>Precision:</strong> Our trained cleaning specialists follow systematic procedures to ensure no detail is overlooked.</li>
  <li><strong>Integrity:</strong> We do what we say we will, every single time. Our veteran background ensures we uphold the highest ethical standards.</li>
</ul>

<h3>Why It Matters for Our Community</h3>
<p>Being a part of The Shoals & Surrounding Areas means contributing positively to our community. Our military-precision accountability goes beyond just cleaning; it's about building trust and ensuring peace of mind for our clients. Here's how our commitment impacts our neighbors:</p>

<h4>Reliability and Trust</h4>
<p>Our clients know that when they hire The Valley Clean Team, they are investing in more than just a cleaning service. They are securing a promise of reliability and trustworthiness, elements that are often missing in the industry.</p>

<h4>Community Focus</h4>
<p>As a local business, we prioritize the needs of our clients in The Shoals & Surrounding Areas. Our veteran-owned status reinforces our dedication to serving and uplifting our community with every service we provide.</p>

<h3>The Benefits of Choosing The Valley Clean Team</h3>
<p>When you choose us, you're not just getting a cleaning service; you're getting a team dedicated to restoring, maintaining, and protecting your home or office with military precision. Here are some benefits you can expect:</p>

<ul>
  <li><strong>Guaranteed Results:</strong> Our systematic approach ensures every job is done right, every time.</li>
  <li><strong>Transparent Pricing:</strong> We offer upfront pricing starting at $125, so you know exactly what to expect.</li>
  <li><strong>Peace of Mind:</strong> With our disciplined approach, you can rest assured knowing your space is in expert hands.</li>
</ul>

<h3>Join Us in Honoring Veterans</h3>
<p>On Veterans Day, we take a moment to honor those who have served our country with dedication and courage. At The Valley Clean Team, we carry these values into our work every day. Our military-precision accountability is our way of paying tribute to the discipline and integrity that our veterans exemplify.</p>

<h3>Reclaim Your Time with Precision and Care</h3>
<p>Your time is valuable, and your home deserves the best care. Book a guaranteed clean with The Valley Clean Team today and experience the difference that military-precision accountability makes. See availability and get your free quote now to reclaim your weekend and enjoy peace of mind in The Shoals & Surrounding Areas.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </article>
  ) : (
    <article class="py-16 bg-white border-t border-gray-100 shadow-inner">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12 bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl">
        <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none text-center">
          <Icon name="clock" class="w-16 h-16 text-[#FFA985] mx-auto mb-6" />
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4 mt-0">Article Coming Soon!</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 m-0">This article is locked and scheduled to automatically publish on <br/><strong class="text-gray-800 text-xl">November 9 2026</strong>.<br/>Check back then!</p>
          <div class="mt-12">
            <a href="/blog" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-6 py-3 text-lg font-semibold text-white bg-[#FFA985] rounded-full hover:bg-[#ff9a70] transition shadow-md no-underline">
              Back to Blog
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </article>
  )}
</BaseLayout>
